import React from "react";
import { Container, Typography, Card, CardContent, Grid, LinearProgress } from "@mui/material";

const skillsData = [
    { title: "JavaScript", level: 90 },
    { title: "React.js", level: 85 },
    { title: "HTML5", level: 90 },
    { title: "CSS3", level: 85 },
    { title: "Java", level: 90 },
    { title: "C", level: 75 },
    { title: "Python", level: 65 },
    { title: "TypeScript", level: 70 },
    { title: "HTML5", level: 95 },
    { title: "CSS", level: 100 },
    { title: "R", level: 80 },
    { title: "MySQL", level: 85 },
    { title: "React-Native", level: 85 },
    { title: "Postman", level: 80 },
    { title: "Git", level: 95 },
    { title: "Linux", level: 70 },
    { title: "Figma", level: 90 },
    { title: "FastAPI", level: 60 },
    { title: "JSON", level: 90 },
    { title: "pgAdmin", level: 80 },
    { title: "Jira", level: 90 },
    { title: "Agile", level: 90 },
    { title: "Node.js", level: 90 },
  ];
  

const Skill = () => {
    return (
        <Container id="intro" sx={{ display: "flex", flexDirection: "column", alignItems: "center", justifyContent: "center", height: "100%" }}>
          <Typography variant="h2" fontWeight={"bold"} align="center" mt={5} mb={3}>
            Skills
          </Typography>
          <Grid container spacing={1}>
            {skillsData.map((skill, index) => (
              <Grid item key={index} xs={12} sm={12} md={12}>
                {/* Set xs, sm, and md to 12 to have only one column */}
                <Card elevation={3}>
                  <CardContent>
                    <Typography variant="h6" color="textSecondary" gutterBottom>
                      {skill.title}
                    </Typography>
                    <LinearProgress variant="determinate" value={skill.level} />
                    <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary" mt={2}>
                      Level: {skill.level}%
                    </Typography>
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </Grid>
            ))}
          </Grid>
        </Container>
      );
};

export default Skill;
